%Steps%

The **Blackboard** is the memory of the **Behavior Tree**. Here we will store a reference to the Actor we should flee from and a location to flee to.

## Steps

1. **Double-click** the Blackboard asset in the **Content Browser**.
1. Using the **New Key** button ![](Engine/AI/BehaviorTrees/QuickStart/5/newKey_button.png),  add a **Vector** key named **FleeToLocation**.
1. Add an **Object** key named **ActorToFleeFrom**.

	![](finalBB.png)

1. Save your Blackboard asset.


